text: Ramindu de Silva (born 16 July 1996) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Nondescripts Cricket Club in the 2016–17 Premier League Tournament on 11 January 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Nondescripts Cricket Club cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Galle
